---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = "Services — SENAVIA Corp · Web Design, Digital Marketing & Development";
const description = "End-to-end digital agency services for South Florida businesses — custom web design, SEO-driven marketing, and scalable web development.";
---
<BaseLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonical="/services"
  jsonLdType="service"
  screenLabel="Services"
>
<main>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO (compact)
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="hero is-compact" data-screen-label="01 Services Hero">
    <video class="hero-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata"
           disablepictureinpicture disableremoteplayback
           controlslist="nodownload nofullscreen noremoteplayback"
           poster="/videos/bg-video-poster.jpg">
      <source src="/videos/bg-video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 18px;"><span class="lang-only-en">What we do</span><span class="lang-only-es">Qué hacemos</span></div>
      <h1><span class="lang-only-en">Digital Agency Services Built for Business Growth</span><span class="lang-only-es">Servicios de Agencia Digital Creados para el Crecimiento de tu Negocio</span></h1>
      <p class="lang-only-en">Three connected practices — Web Design, Digital Marketing, and Web Development — combined into a single growth system. We build the site, drive the traffic, and engineer the systems that scale your South Florida business.</p>
      <p class="lang-only-es">Tres prácticas conectadas — Diseño Web, Marketing Digital y Desarrollo Web — combinadas en un solo sistema de crecimiento. Construimos el sitio, atraemos el tráfico y diseñamos los sistemas que escalan su negocio en el Sur de Florida.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn" onclick="if(window.Calendly){Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/leads-senaviacorp/30-minute-meeting-clon'});}return false;"><span class="lang-only-en">Book a Free Call</span><span class="lang-only-es">Agenda tu Llamada Gratis</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       SERVICES — detailed 3 cards
       ============================================================ -->
  <section id="services" class="section section--band" data-screen-label="02 Services Detail">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="lang-only-en">The 3 pillars</span><span class="lang-only-es">Los 3 pilares</span></div>
        <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Digital Services Designed To Grow Your Business In South Florida</span><span class="lang-only-es">Servicios Digitales Diseñados Para Hacer Crecer su Negocio en el Sur de Florida</span></h2>
        <p class="lang-only-en">From custom web design to digital marketing and custom software development — SENAVIA Corp delivers end-to-end digital solutions that help South Florida businesses attract more customers, rank higher on Google, and scale revenue faster.</p>
        <p class="lang-only-es">Desde diseño web a la medida hasta marketing digital y desarrollo de software personalizado — SENAVIA Corp ofrece soluciones digitales integrales que ayudan a los negocios del Sur de Florida a atraer más clientes, posicionarse mejor en Google y escalar sus ingresos más rápido.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3 services-detailed" data-reveal-children>

        <article class="card-border is-purple">
          <a class="card-glass service-link" href="/services/web-design">
            <span class="svc-icon"><img src="/images/Web-Design-Icon.svg" alt=""></span>
            <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Web Design</span><span class="lang-only-es">Diseño Web</span></h3>
            <p class="svc-tagline lang-only-en">Modern, responsive, SEO-optimized websites that convert visitors into customers and strengthen brand authority across South Florida.</p>
            <p class="svc-tagline lang-only-es">Sitios web modernos, responsivos y optimizados para SEO que convierten visitantes en clientes y fortalecen la autoridad de marca en todo el Sur de Florida.</p>
            <ul class="svc-list lang-only-en">
              <li>Custom UX &amp; UI design</li>
              <li>Webflow &amp; CMS builds</li>
              <li>E-commerce on Shopify</li>
              <li>Core Web Vitals tuning</li>
              <li>Conversion-rate optimization</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="svc-list lang-only-es">
              <li>Diseño UX &amp; UI a la medida</li>
              <li>Desarrollos en Webflow &amp; CMS</li>
              <li>E-commerce en Shopify</li>
              <li>Optimización de Core Web Vitals</li>
              <li>Optimización de la tasa de conversión</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="more"><span class="lang-only-en">Explore Web Design</span><span class="lang-only-es">Explora Diseño Web</span></span>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card-border is-cyan">
          <a class="card-glass service-link" href="/services/digital-marketing">
            <span class="svc-icon is-cyan"><img src="/images/Marketing-Icon.svg" alt=""></span>
            <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Digital Marketing</span><span class="lang-only-es">Marketing Digital</span></h3>
            <p class="svc-tagline lang-only-en">SEO, Google Ads, and data-driven marketing strategies that attract qualified traffic and generate leads for local businesses.</p>
            <p class="svc-tagline lang-only-es">SEO, Google Ads y estrategias de marketing basadas en datos que atraen tráfico calificado y generan clientes potenciales para negocios locales.</p>
            <ul class="svc-list lang-only-en">
              <li>Local SEO &amp; Google Business Profile</li>
              <li>Google Ads &amp; Meta Ads</li>
              <li>Technical SEO &amp; schema</li>
              <li>Content &amp; AEO strategy</li>
              <li>Analytics &amp; attribution</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="svc-list lang-only-es">
              <li>SEO local &amp; Perfil de Negocio de Google</li>
              <li>Google Ads &amp; Meta Ads</li>
              <li>SEO técnico &amp; schema</li>
              <li>Estrategia de contenido &amp; AEO</li>
              <li>Analítica &amp; atribución</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="more"><span class="lang-only-en">Explore Marketing</span><span class="lang-only-es">Explora Marketing</span></span>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card-border is-green">
          <a class="card-glass service-link" href="/services/web-development">
            <span class="svc-icon is-green"><img src="/images/Development-Icon.svg" alt=""></span>
            <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Web Development</span><span class="lang-only-es">Desarrollo Web</span></h3>
            <p class="svc-tagline lang-only-en">Scalable web solutions in Webflow, Shopify, and custom systems — engineered for performance, conversion, and growth.</p>
            <p class="svc-tagline lang-only-es">Soluciones web escalables en Webflow, Shopify y sistemas personalizados — diseñadas para el rendimiento, la conversión y el crecimiento.</p>
            <ul class="svc-list lang-only-en">
              <li>Custom web applications</li>
              <li>API &amp; CRM integrations</li>
              <li>Internal admin panels</li>
              <li>Automation &amp; workflows</li>
              <li>Headless CMS architectures</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="svc-list lang-only-es">
              <li>Aplicaciones web a la medida</li>
              <li>Integraciones de API &amp; CRM</li>
              <li>Paneles administrativos internos</li>
              <li>Automatización &amp; flujos de trabajo</li>
              <li>Arquitecturas headless CMS</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="more"><span class="lang-only-en">Explore Development</span><span class="lang-only-es">Explora Desarrollo</span></span>
          </a>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       PROCESS (inside green-bg)
       ============================================================ -->
  <div class="green-bg">
    <img class="figure f1" src="/images/figure-bg-3.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="figure f2" src="/images/figure-bg-2.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="figure f3" src="/images/figure-bg-1.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">

    <section id="process" class="section" data-screen-label="03 Process">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <div class="eyebrow"><span class="lang-only-en">How we work</span><span class="lang-only-es">Cómo trabajamos</span></div>
          <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Our Process</span><span class="lang-only-es">Nuestro Proceso</span></h2>
          <p class="lang-only-en">We understand your goals and challenges, create a tailored plan with clear estimates, and build a custom solution designed for your success.</p>
          <p class="lang-only-es">Entendemos sus objetivos y desafíos, creamos un plan a la medida con estimaciones claras y construimos una solución personalizada diseñada para su éxito.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-4" data-reveal-children>
          <article class="process-block">
            <img class="process-img" src="/images/process/explore.avif" alt="Digital strategy and market discovery for South Florida businesses" loading="lazy">
            <div class="process-glass"></div>
            <div class="process-content">
              <div class="process-header">
                <h3><span class="lang-only-en">1. Explore</span><span class="lang-only-es">1. Explorar</span></h3>
                <h4><span class="lang-only-en">Digital Strategy &amp; Market Discovery</span><span class="lang-only-es">Estrategia Digital &amp; Descubrimiento de Mercado</span></h4>
              </div>
              <p class="lang-only-en">We analyze goals, audience, and market to uncover growth opportunities across South Florida.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Analizamos objetivos, audiencia y mercado para descubrir oportunidades de crecimiento en todo el Sur de Florida.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="process-block">
            <img class="process-img" src="/images/process/estimate.avif" alt="Project planning and strategic roadmap for a web project" loading="lazy">
            <div class="process-glass"></div>
            <div class="process-content">
              <div class="process-header">
                <h3><span class="lang-only-en">2. Estimate</span><span class="lang-only-es">2. Estimar</span></h3>
                <h4><span class="lang-only-en">Project Planning &amp; Strategic Roadmap</span><span class="lang-only-es">Planificación del Proyecto &amp; Hoja de Ruta Estratégica</span></h4>
              </div>
              <p class="lang-only-en">We define a clear project plan aligned with your budget, timeline, and objectives.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Definimos un plan de proyecto claro alineado con su presupuesto, cronograma y objetivos.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="process-block">
            <img class="process-img" src="/images/process/development.avif" alt="Custom web development and SEO build in progress" loading="lazy">
            <div class="process-glass"></div>
            <div class="process-content">
              <div class="process-header">
                <h3><span class="lang-only-en">3. Development</span><span class="lang-only-es">3. Desarrollo</span></h3>
                <h4><span class="lang-only-en">Custom Web Development &amp; SEO</span><span class="lang-only-es">Desarrollo Web a la Medida &amp; SEO</span></h4>
              </div>
              <p class="lang-only-en">We build high-performance websites and platforms optimized for SEO and conversions.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Construimos sitios web y plataformas de alto rendimiento optimizados para SEO y conversiones.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="process-block">
            <img class="process-img" src="/images/process/delivery.avif" alt="Website launch and ongoing optimization in Plantation, FL" loading="lazy">
            <div class="process-glass"></div>
            <div class="process-content">
              <div class="process-header">
                <h3><span class="lang-only-en">4. Delivery</span><span class="lang-only-es">4. Entrega</span></h3>
                <h4><span class="lang-only-en">Website Launch &amp; Ongoing Optimization</span><span class="lang-only-es">Lanzamiento del Sitio &amp; Optimización Continua</span></h4>
              </div>
              <p class="lang-only-en">We launch and optimize your digital presence from Plantation, serving South Florida.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Lanzamos y optimizamos su presencia digital desde Plantation, sirviendo a todo el Sur de Florida.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="center-cta" style="margin-top: 3rem;" data-reveal>
          <a href="#" class="btn" onclick="if(window.Calendly){Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/leads-senaviacorp/30-minute-meeting-clon'});}return false;"><span class="lang-only-en">Book a Free Call</span><span class="lang-only-es">Agenda tu Llamada Gratis</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CTA
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="cta" data-screen-label="04 CTA">
    <video class="cta-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata"
           disablepictureinpicture disableremoteplayback
           controlslist="nodownload nofullscreen noremoteplayback"
           poster="/videos/cta-bg-poster.jpg">
      <source src="/videos/cta-bg.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
    <div class="container">
      <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Let's Build Your Next Digital Success Story</span><span class="lang-only-es">Construyamos su Próxima Historia de Éxito Digital</span></h2>
      <p class="lang-only-en">Schedule your free web design &amp; SEO consultation and get a custom strategy to increase traffic, leads, and conversions.</p>
      <p class="lang-only-es">Agende su consulta gratuita de diseño web &amp; SEO y obtenga una estrategia personalizada para aumentar el tráfico, los clientes potenciales y las conversiones.</p>
      <a href="tel:+17542623659" class="btn is-call">(754) 262-3659</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</BaseLayout>
